{% set notes %}
<bolt-ol>
  <bolt-li>Setting a string in <bolt-code-snippet display="inline">status.views</bolt-code-snippet> will display the results on the same line as the like and share buttons.</bolt-li>
  <bolt-li>Setting <bolt-code-snippet display="inline">type: 'button',</bolt-code-snippet> in <bolt-code-snippet display="inline">like_button_attributes</bolt-code-snippet> is required to display the like button correctly.</bolt-li>
  <bolt-li>Use the share component to render a menu and pass it into <bolt-code-snippet display="inline">share_menu</bolt-code-snippet>. It will be displayed in a popover.</bolt-li>
</bolt-ol>
{% endset %}

